From 5afd56658b319e8e1ddeed3a83c6fc92153fdadc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude Sandbox <claude@sandbox.local>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 15:46:14 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Phase 2: contacts/FAQ, cart, wishlist, account, newsletter
 popup, horse transition, product catalog
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add /contacts, /shop, /account, /wishlist routes with brand-consistent styling
- Add CartContext + WishlistContext with localStorage persistence
- Add product catalog (src/data/products.js) with 7 SVG placeholder illustrations
- Products page: category filter (Hermès-style), add-to-bag, wishlist heart, toast confirmation
- Shop page: full cart, quantity controls, checkout form, order confirmation
- Wishlist page: shared state with heart icons on Products, add-to-bag from wishlist
- Newsletter popup: burgundy/plum card, cream text, localStorage-once, updated copy
- Footer: '10% discount' subline, Get in Touch + Company grouped as sub-columns
- Navbar icons wired to /wishlist, /account, /shop
- DropdownMenu 'CONTACTS' links to /contacts, closes on navigation
- HorseTransition overlay on route changes (skips initial load)
- ThreeProducts uses catalog images, click through to /products
- Home hero quote updated to 'Equestrian elegance, shaped by Italian craftsmanship.'
